        <div class="sidebar-box">
        <h2>About US</h2>
        <p style="text-align:justify">

            Founded in 2020, Knowmed Samiti is committed to delivering high-quality publishing solutions to researchers, academicians, scholars, institutional libraries, students, and affiliated professionals. We specialize in publishing peer-reviewed research across the fields of medicine, nursing, pharmacy, and other health sciences through both print and online open-access journals.<br />
            Headquartered in Haryana, India, Knowmed Samiti upholds the highest standards of academic publishing, ensuring the integrity, accessibility, and global reach of scholarly work.<br />
            We are proud members with Crossref, for the assignment of Digital Object Identifiers (DOIs) to ensure persistent and reliable citation of published articles, Plagiarism X, to conduct comprehensive plagiarism checks and maintain the originality of all submissions before publication and Open Journal Systems (OJS), for the digital archiving and long-term preservation of published content.<br />
            Knowmed Samiti is an open-access publishing platform, offering free and unrestricted online access to all research outputs, including journal articles and books. There are no subscription fees or registration requirements—all content is made immediately available upon publication.<br />
            Our open-access policy ensures that researchers, scholars, students, and readers worldwide can easily access and benefit from the latest scientific knowledge. This model not only supports the global exchange of information but also enhances the visibility, reach, and citation of the research we publish, contributing to greater academic impact.<br />
        </p>
