            <p style="text-align:justify">
            At Knowmed Samiti, our journals operate on an open-access platform, reflecting our commitment to making quality scientific research freely available to the global community. We aim to bridge the gap between high-quality research and worldwide audiences, including researchers, scholars, academicians, institutional and academic libraries, students, and affiliated professionals.
        </p>
